\p
\v 18 What profiteth the graven image that the maker thereof hath graven it;
the molten image, and a teacher of lies, that the maker of his work trusteth
therein, to make dumb idols? 
\v 19 Woe unto him that saith to the wood, Awake; to the dumb stone, Arise, it
